## ğŸš€ Quick Start

```bash
# Clone the repository
git clone https://github.com/your-username/fakestore-ecommerce-clone.git
cd fakestore-ecommerce-clone

# Install dependencies
pip install requests

# Run the scraper
python main.py

# Open the UI
start index.html   # or open index.html manually in browser
````

